::Feline::

She chuckled a little as he kissed her nose.  She wrapped her arm 
around his as they walked towards the entrance.  She was purring, not 
only for him, but because she was enjoying herself. She wasn't sure 
how te assignment would go at first, but she had under estimated 
herself.  Allwas going smoothly for her.  She wondered how Skulletron 
was doing on his end of things.

> 
> Chordate chuckled softly, kissing Feline on the nose.  "It is a

to

a 
> few more cycles needed to get out of the Cybertronian Fire.
